msgstr ""
".. image:: images/brush-tips/Krita-brushtips-caustics_13.png\n"
"   :alt: 最後の仕上げ。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/caustics.rst:94
msgid "Final Result"
msgstr "出来上がった作品"

